ce:section.ce:para:
The chromaticity coordinates of ANP with varying concentrations of NANA added to the CIE moved in a straight line from red to blue area, indicating the feasibility of visual semi-quantitative detection. ANP containing different concentrations of NANA were sequentially placed in a cuvette and observed under an UV lamp (λ
                        ex = 254 nm), the color information of the pictures was digitized using the color analysis software on the smartphone and the RGB values were analyzed (Fig. 6
                        ). The B/R values showed a good linear relationship with the concentration of NANA (1–4 mM and 4–10 mM). The LOD of NANA by the visual detection platform was 0.09 mM.
